ENTRY            A0587   20260202   20260327   20260327       A130
SUBENT        A0587001   20260202   20260327   20260327       A130
BIB                 10         20
TITLE      Cross sections of barium isotopes in the interaction of
           60 MeV/nucleon 18O with 238U
AUTHOR     (Xu Yanbing, Yang Weifan, Yuan Shuanggui, Xiao Yonghou,
           Pan Qiangyan, Li Yingjun)
INSTITUTE  (3CPRIMP)
REFERENCE  (J,JRN,251,341,2002)
SAMPLE     Natural U target (50 mg/cm2)
DETECTOR   (HPGE) Gamma-ray detector with an efficiency of 70%
           and an energy resolution of 2.6 keV (FWHM) for the
           1.33 MeV line of 60Co.
FACILITY   (CYCLO,3CPRIMP) Heavy Ion Research Facility
METHOD     (EXTB) The 60 MeV/u 18O beam
           (ACTIV) Beam current intensity of 30-40 nA was used
           to irradiate target for 30 and 120 min.
           (GSPEC)
STATUS     (TABLE,,Xu Yanbing+,J,JRN,251,341,2002) Table 1.
HISTORY    (20031003C)
           (20040213U) Last checking has been done.
           (20260202A) SD: BIB updated. Value in col.EN changed
           according to presentation in the article.
ENDBIB              20
COMMON               1          3
EN
MEV/A
       60.
ENDCOMMON            3
